'''aksil''' (s talatinit: Caecilius), iga agellid [[imaziɣen|amaziɣ]] d amɣar ameqqran n twsit (taqbilt) tawrabt, ilul g tɣrmt n [[xncla]] g tmurt n [[dzayr]] ، ynbḍ tagldit tamaziɣt [[ttafa]] nna  ysmun [[dzayr]] d igzzumn sg tuns، yumẓ wakal n tgldit nns  jar tahrt (tayart )  d wahran d tlmsan g utaram ar [[qayrawan]] g ugmuḍ.  ittuyssan aṭṭas g uzmz n ukccum n waɛrabn ɣr [[tafriqt n ugafa|tfrikt n ugafa]]. ifl [[tamasiḥit|tamasiḥit]] ikcm ɣr [[islam|lislm]].  

immnɣa aksil mgal isrdasn n [[ɛqba n nafiɛ]]   d isrdasn n [[qays bn  zuhayr abalwi]]،

tga tsrtit n [[abu almuhajir dinar]] dg tɣrmt n [[lqayrawan]] tɛkks d imaziɣn tiwi ɣr wuɣal n isfka d idrimn ssnbḍn [[imawiyn]]   [[ɛqba n nafiɛ]] ɣaf tɣrmt n [[qayrawan]] g usggas  62 ahijri /681 ، ssxcn aɛrabn i [[imaziɣn]]  
igul ugllid aksil s intiqam. dffir uya ylla imnɣi jar aɛrabn d imaziɣn g [[tbskrt]] anẓul n [[idurar n awras]] s usrdas yiwḍ uṭṭun nns nig n 50,0000 n usrdas  amɣar nnsn agllid aksil، rnawn imaziɣn [[aɛrabn]] g imnɣi da, ymmut ɛqba n nafɛ   asggas n 64 ahijri 684 n tlalit n ɛisa،   .dffir arnaw، ybna aksil tagldit tamqqrant  tlla sg  dzayr ar [[tuns]]، sg [[idurar n awras]] ar [[qsṭinṭina]] d [[qayrawan]] tamaẓunt n [[tuns]] tazaykut    . innurẓm aksil amslay d irumiyn.




